\c 1
\s Nzira yevakarurama nenzira yevasakarurama
\p
\v 1 Wakaropafadzwa munhu asingafambi pakurangana kwevakaipa, uye asingamiri panzira yevatadzi, uye asingagari pachigaro chevashoori.
\v 2 Asi mufaro wake uri pamurau waJehovha, uye anofungisisa murau wake masikati neusiku.
\v 3 Zvino achafanana nemuti wakasimwa pahova dzemvura, unopa muchero wawo panguva yawo, shizha rawo haringasvavi; nechose chaanoita chichabudirira.
\p
\v 4 Vakaipa havana kudaro, asi \add vaka\add*fanana nehundi mhepo yainopeperesa.
\v 5 Naizvozvo vakaipa havangamiri pakutongwa, nevatadzi paungano yevakarurama.
\p
\v 6 Nokuti Jehovha anoziva nzira yevakarurama; asi nzira yevakaipa ichaparara.